name: Parallel Universe Planet Project #2
description:
Parallel Universe Planet Project is a series of interactive artwork projects for P5JS. Each planet has its own unique physical rules.

Planet #2 is a blue planet made of pure dust. The viewer can click on the screen to produce dots of dust and rings to form the planet.

Because Planet #2 has a strange energy field, lines of blue energy will be produced as the dust approaches, outlining the planet's appearance.
